  "body": "<center>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6468a26c95c48f0a1b4df941\" />\r\n<br /><br />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6401ef2c4526c830844a5bab\" /><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/plugin/kudos/versions\"><img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6401f3254526c830844a5bb7\" /></a><a href=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/wiki/MTKudos/\"><img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6401f3254526c830844a5bb9\" /></a><a href=\"https://discord.gg/FdMjWSP\"><img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6401f3254526c830844a5bba\" /></a>\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/65db738493401d34a215157d\" />\r\n<br>\r\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/65db738493401d34a215157b\" />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/FdMjWSP\"><img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/638a91e9aa2989386ab8ef79\" /> </a>\r\n\r\n<details>\r\n<summary>Full transcript</summary>\r\nMTKudos\r\n\r\nCUSTOMIZABLE REWARDS\r\nOffers a flexible and customizable reward system \r\n\r\nFully customizable, allowing you to create rewards with unique names and descriptions.\r\nCustomize reward commands with placeholders.\r\n\r\nLEADERBOARD\r\nHighlight your server's most helpful players\r\nShowcase player progress.\r\n\r\nA simple and nice looking leaderboard!\r\n\r\nCOOLDOWN\r\nControl spam with Kudos cooldowns!\r\nControl how often players can give and receive Kudos.\r\n   \r\nPrevent abuse & keep things fair.\r\n\r\nPERMISSION \r\nControl who can give and receive Kudos with ease!\r\n\r\nAlows you to fine-tune every aspect of the plugin to suit your needs.\r\n\r\nEasy-to-Use Commands!\r\n</details>\r\n\r\n</center>\r\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/views/HiQiEgsbOg8_EyIDNwIACRscaTcmHwMDKh0MCRs\" />",
